Interface SampledTrainable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Trainable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConstL12Normalizer, SampledArrayTrainable, SampledCachedTrainable

    public interface SampledTrainable
extends Trainable
    A trainable contract for variable sample size; smaller values result in faster but less representative evaluations.
